# Settings domain

## Required for first timetable

1. User-chosen **calculation method** (explicit, first run)
2. **Location** (GPS or saved city) + timezone

Expose `SetupCompletionStatus`: `isCalculationConfigured`, `isLocationConfigured`.

## Calculation (maps to adhan_dart)

- Method presets: MWL, ISNA, Karachi, Egyptian, Umm Al-Qura, Dubai, Qatar, Kuwait, Singapore, Turkey, Tehran, Jafari, Moonsighting, North America, Custom
- Madhab: Shafi (default) / Hanafi (Asr only)
- High-latitude rule: middle of night / one-seventh / twilight angle
- Custom: fajr/isha/maghrib angles, isha interval minutes
- Per-prayer minute adjustments + global offset
- Conditional UI: Shafaq when method = Moonsighting; custom angles when method = Custom

## Display & app

- Time format 12h/24h, language, theme, Hijri adjustment (−2..+2)
- Notifications: master + per-prayer; MVP sound = system default only

## Persistence

- Canonical enums in domain; single mapper to `CalculationParameters`
- Reserve API adapter fields for v2 (Aladhan/IslamicFinder) without breaking local-first MVP
